# UIDefaultLaunchStoryboard

**Property List Key**

The identifier of the default launch storyboard to use.

## Specifying Launch Storyboards

- **UILaunchStoryboardDefinitions**: An array of dictionaries mapping launch storyboard identifiers to storyboards.
